'''热罗尼莫·卡瓦略·德索萨'''（{{lang-pt|Jerónimo Carvalho de Sousa}}；{{bd|1947年|4月13日}}）是一位[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]政治家。

==生平==
2004年11月，他在[[葡萄牙共产党|葡萄牙共产党]]第十七次代表大会当选为葡萄牙共产党总书记，担任该职务至今。<ref name=twsDecG28>{{cite news
 |author= RAPHAEL MINDER
 |title= Like Spain, Portugal Hopes to Make Cuts, but It Is Mired in Structural Weakness
 |publisher= ''The New York Times: Global Business''
 |quote= In Portugal, smaller political parties also urged resistance. Jerónimo de Sousa, head of the Communist Party, said on Portuguese television that “people have to react with protest and struggle.”
 |date= May 13, 2010
 |url= http://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/14/business/global/14portugal.html
 |accessdate= 2010-12-07
 |archive-date= 2020-09-19
 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200919075645/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/14/business/global/14portugal.html
 |dead-url= no
 }}</ref>

他还是一名[[共和国议会_(葡萄牙)|葡萄牙共和国议会]]议员，并曾作为[[联合民主联盟|联合民主联盟]]候选人参加[[2006年葡萄牙总统选举|2006年葡萄牙总统选举]]。

